        <div class="location-dir">Cll 7d # 43c - 134, Medellín, Antioquia - <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Factor%C3%ADa+HUB/@6.2094431,-75.5763395,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x8e44282ad3055b19:0xc79fa2d4c3232f1b!8m2!3d6.2094431!4d-75.5741508" target="_blank">Google Maps</a></div>
